a decrease of platelet count and a reduction in cardiovascular risk levels were 
observed in the older population. Immune activation markers expressed 
on CD4+ T cells decreased compared to baseline, but this difference was greater 
in the control group.Conclusion: A 60-month treatment with 
RAL-containing regimens is safe and highly effective in the older PLWH and these 
data give new insights on the elderly population.Clinical trial registration: 
NCT02765776 and NCT03579485.

